Text: Hey, do you wanna hear a braindead and exploited kid with no talents at all? Then you've come to the right place! This is freakish psycho-mainstream, a fluke which will be forgotten in your next heartbeat. Behind this kid-puppet is probably his parents or older brother, looking to make a fast buck - did someone say "cynical"? Put it in the rubbish and wash your ears if you hear it, probably played by some braindead radiostation dishing out shit by the minute.
